Subject: [PATCH] ext_lm_group_acl: Improved username handling (#512)

---
 helpers/external_acl/LM_group/ext_lm_group_acl.cc | 6 +++---
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/helpers/external_acl/LM_group/ext_lm_group_acl.cc b/helpers/external_acl/LM_group/ext_lm_group_acl.cc
index def9db5ff..f93fc33e4 100644
